- **Google Analytics:** [tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout](https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout)
- **Microsoft Clarity:** [privacy.microsoft.com](https://privacy.microsoft.com/nl-nl/privacystatement)

